Grace Matthews https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grace_Matthews 0 Grace Matthews (September 3, 1910 – May 15, 1995) was an actress in the era of old-time radio and the early years of television. She is perhaps best known for portraying Margo Lane in the radio program The Shadow.
